Get ready for the grandest beauty event of the year – Lucknow Mega Beauty Expo 2025 (Season 02), happening on 30th & 31st July 2025 at Dayal Gateway, Kisaan Bazar Convention Centre, Lucknow.

Experience the City’s Biggest Beauty Festival, organized by Ice Burst Entertainment, featuring top brands, live demos, and exclusive showcases.

Don't miss the Live Makeup Demo by Mohit Kumar (MUA) – International Makeup Educator – on 30th July from 2 PM to 3 PM at Stall No. 31, powered by MS Glamour and Cosmos Hub.

Special appearance by Celebrity Guest Mannara Chopra, Indian TV and Bollywood Actress.

Title Sponsor: Velvetree
Brush Partner: London Prime
Beverage Partner: Coca-Cola

Free Registration available via AllEvents.
For more info: +91 75210 97811

Nomination Open Now for awards and participation. Be there to witness beauty, talent, and glamour like never before.
